  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CROSS-PLATFORM MULTIPLAYER & OFFLINE PLAY</h2>5 players per race, different modes, lots of maps.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/944f822716d46cace2963da14596ab29.poster.avif?t=1573935974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/944f822716d46cace2963da14596ab29.webm?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/944f822716d46cace2963da14596ab29.mp4?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Try our arsenal of weapons, while mastering the mesmerizing, stunning tracks of other planets.<br></li><li>The high-speed hover physics lets you clear the track with insane speed and feel.<br></li><li>Shields, turbos, missiles and traps you got them all, with multiple online and offline game modes.<br></li><li>Rush to victory in MONSTER HUNT a unique game mode, never seen in combat racing games before.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OFFLINE CAMPAIGN MODE</h2>Increasing difficulty on every map, to play when you are offline.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/2b0fdcf5bc349383040a64f950a534bc.poster.avif?t=1573935974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/2b0fdcf5bc349383040a64f950a534bc.webm?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/2b0fdcf5bc349383040a64f950a534bc.mp4?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAUTIFUL WORLDS TO EXPLORE WHILE RACING</h2>But don't get too distracted!<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/015f587db5ee11ed647ea4887187da67.poster.avif?t=1573935974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/015f587db5ee11ed647ea4887187da67.webm?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/015f587db5ee11ed647ea4887187da67.mp4?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBAT AND STRATEGY</h2>Not just the speed, but weapons and tactics decide who will be the winner.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/31eac639cbbe571edd4ce1e56314cef1.poster.avif?t=1573935974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/31eac639cbbe571edd4ce1e56314cef1.webm?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/31eac639cbbe571edd4ce1e56314cef1.mp4?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2>Unlock all power-ups and upgrade your vehicle to be the strongest.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/396b2e370c1d4306bbb08f945e143daf.poster.avif?t=1573935974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779450/extras/396b2e370c1d4306bbb08f945e143daf.webm?t=1573935974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"htt